<Layout
  title="AI 스킬 — 마이너스베타스튜디오"
  description={`Claude와 Codex에서 반복 업무를 재사용하는 ${skills.length}개 AI 스킬. 구상, 제작, 배차, 운영, 발행 흐름과 실행 환경별로 탐색합니다.`}
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <meta property="og:title" content="AI 스킬 — 마이너스베타스튜디오" />
    <meta
      property="og:description"
      content="구상부터 제작, 배차, 운영, 발행까지 반복 업무를 재사용하는 Claude/Codex 스킬 아카이브."
    />
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://work.kangdaejong.com/og-default.png" />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://work.kangdaejong.com/skills.html" />
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="강대종 작업장" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="AI 스킬 — 마이너스베타스튜디오" />
    <meta
      name="twitter:description"
      content="구상부터 제작, 배차, 운영, 발행까지 반복 업무를 재사용하는 Claude/Codex 스킬 아카이브."
    />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://work.kangdaejong.com/og-default.png" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://work.kangdaejong.com/skills.html" />
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)} />
  </Fragment>

  <article class="skills-page">
    <header class="skills-hero" aria-labelledby="page-title">
      <div class="hero-copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">REUSABLE AI WORKFLOWS</p>
        <h1 id="page-title">AI 스킬</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          반복 업무를 한 번의 명령으로 다시 쓰는 작업 루틴입니다. 아이디어를 다듬는 순간부터
          여러 노드에 일을 나누고, 결과를 발행하고, 하루를 닫는 순간까지 이어집니다.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-side">
        <dl class="hero-stats" aria-label="AI 스킬 요약">
          <div>
            <dt>활성</dt>
            <dd>{skills.length}<small>skills</small></dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>흐름</dt>
            <dd>{laneDefinitions.length}<small>lanes</small></dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>실행면</dt>
            <dd>{surfaceDefinitions.length}<small>surfaces</small></dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
        <p class="surface-summary">
          Mac {surfaceCounts.get('mac')} · WSL {surfaceCounts.get('wsl')} · Codex {surfaceCounts.get('codex')}
        </p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <aside class="update-note" aria-label="최근 변경">
      <span class="update-label">RECENT UPDATE</span>
      <p>
        <time datetime="2026-07-22">2026.07.22</time>
        <span>공개 스킬 목록 현행화</span>
        <span>Flutter 5종 · verify 3종 · claude-fleet-update · playwright-login-session 추가</span>
      </p>
    </aside>

    <section class="lane-section" data-lane-section aria-labelledby="lane-title">
      <div class="section-head">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">WORKFLOW MAP</p>
          <h2 id="lane-title">어떤 일을 하려는지부터 고릅니다.</h2>
        </div>
        <p>스킬 이름을 외우기보다 지금 하려는 일의 흐름에서 출발하도록 다섯 갈래로 묶었습니다.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="lane-grid">
        {
          laneDefinitions.map((lane) => (
            <button type="button" class="lane-card" data-lane-shortcut={lane.id}>
              <span class="lane-topline">
                <span>{lane.number}</span>
                <span>{laneCounts.get(lane.id)} skills</span>
              </span>
              <span class="lane-eyebrow">{lane.eyebrow}</span>
              <strong>{lane.label}</strong>
              <span class="lane-description">{lane.description}</span>
              <span class="lane-arrow" aria-hidden="true">↓</span>
            </button>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="catalog-section" aria-labelledby="catalog-title">
      <div class="section-head catalog-head">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">SKILL INDEX</p>
          <h2 id="catalog-title">전체 스킬</h2>
        </div>
        <p>이름과 설명을 검색하고, 실행면과 작업 흐름을 함께 조합해 필요한 루틴을 찾습니다.</p>
      </div>

      <form class="filter-panel" data-filter-form role="search">
        <div class="filter-field search-field">
          <label for="skill-search">스킬 검색</label>
          <div class="input-shell">
            <span aria-hidden="true">⌕</span>
            <input
              id="skill-search"
              data-search-input
              type="search"
              inputmode="search"
              autocomplete="off"
              placeholder="예: Flutter, 발행, 브레인스토밍"
              aria-describedby="filter-status"
            />
            <kbd aria-hidden="true">/</kbd>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="filter-field">
          <label for="surface-filter">실행면</label>
          <select id="surface-filter" data-surface-select aria-describedby="filter-status">
            <option value="">전체 실행면</option>
            {surfaceDefinitions.map((surface) => (
              <option value={surface.id}>{surface.label} · {surfaceCounts.get(surface.id)}</option>
            ))}
          </select>
        </div>

        <div class="filter-field">
          <label for="lane-filter">작업 흐름</label>
          <select id="lane-filter" data-lane-select aria-describedby="filter-status">
            <option value="">전체 흐름</option>
            {laneDefinitions.map((lane) => (
              <option value={lane.id}>{lane.label} · {laneCounts.get(lane.id)}</option>
            ))}
          </select>
        </div>

        <button class="reset-button" type="reset">초기화</button>
      </form>

      <div class="lane-rail" aria-label="작업 흐름 바로가기">
        <button class="lane-chip is-active" type="button" data-lane-chip="" aria-pressed="true">
          전체 <span>{skills.length}</span>
        </button>
        {laneDefinitions.map((lane) => (
          <button
            class="lane-chip"
            type="button"
            data-lane-chip={lane.id}
            aria-pressed="false"
          >
            {lane.label} <span>{laneCounts.get(lane.id)}</span>
          </button>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="catalog-toolbar">
        <p id="filter-status" data-filter-status aria-live="polite">전체 {skills.length}개</p>
        <a href="#skill-changelog">변동사항 보기</a>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-grid" data-skill-grid>
        {
          skills.map((skill, index) => {
            const lane = laneMap.get(skill.lane);
            const searchText = [
              skill.name,
              skill.tag,
              lane?.label,
              lane?.eyebrow,
              skill.description,
              ...skill.surfaces.map((surface) => surfaceMap.get(surface)?.label),
            ]
              .filter(Boolean)
              .join(' ')
              .toLocaleLowerCase('ko-KR');

            return (
              <article
                class="skill-card"
                data-skill-entry
                data-lane={skill.lane}
                data-surfaces={skill.surfaces.join(' ')}
                data-search={searchText}
              >
                <a
                  href={skillHref(skill.name)}
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener"
                  aria-label={'/' + skill.name + ' 원문을 GitHub에서 열기'}
                >
                  <span class="skill-topline">
                    <span>{String(index + 1).padStart(2, '0')}</span>
                    <span>{lane?.eyebrow}</span>
                  </span>
                  <span class="skill-title-row">
                    <h3>/{skill.name}</h3>
                    {skill.isNew && <span class="new-badge">NEW</span>}
                  </span>
                  <span class="skill-tag">{skill.tag}</span>
                  <p>{skill.description}</p>
                  <span class="skill-footer">
                    <span class="surface-list" aria-label="지원 실행면">
                      {skill.surfaces.map((surface) => {
                        const definition = surfaceMap.get(surface);
                        return (
                          <span title={definition?.label}>
                            <b>{definition?.mark}</b>{definition?.label}
                          </span>
                        );
                      })}
                    </span>
                    <span class="github-link">GitHub <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span></span>
                  </span>
                </a>
              </article>
            );
          })
        }
      </div>

      <div class="empty-state" data-empty-state hidden>
        <strong>일치하는 스킬이 없습니다.</strong>
        <p>검색어를 줄이거나 실행면과 작업 흐름을 전체로 바꿔보세요.</p>
        <button type="button" data-empty-reset>필터 초기화</button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <details class="changelog" id="skill-changelog">
      <summary>
        <span>
          <span class="eyebrow">CHANGELOG</span>
          <strong>스킬 변동사항</strong>
        </span>
        <span>2026.07.22 latest <b aria-hidden="true">＋</b></span>
      </summary>
      <div class="changelog-body">
        {changelog.map((group) => (
          <section class="change-group">
            <header>
              <h3>{group.date}</h3>
              <span>{group.items.length} changes</span>
            </header>
            <ol>
              {group.items.map(([kind, name, reason]) => (
                <li>
                  <span class={'change-badge change-' + kind}>
                    {kind === 'new' ? '신규' : kind === 'edit' ? '수정' : '삭제'}
                  </span>
                  <code>/{name}</code>
                  <p>{reason}</p>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ol>
          </section>
        ))}
      </div>
    </details>

    <footer class="skills-footer">
      <p>공개 목록 마지막 갱신 2026.07.22 · 활성 스킬 {skills.length}개</p>
      <a href="/system">system으로 돌아가기</a>
    </footer>
  </article>

  <script is:inline>
    (() => {
      const form = document.querySelector('[data-filter-form]');
      const searchInput = document.querySelector('[data-search-input]');
      const surfaceSelect = document.querySelector('[data-surface-select]');
      const laneSelect = document.querySelector('[data-lane-select]');
      const status = document.querySelector('[data-filter-status]');
      const cards = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('[data-skill-entry]'));
      const laneChips = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('[data-lane-chip]'));
      const laneShortcuts = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('[data-lane-shortcut]'));
      const emptyState = document.querySelector('[data-empty-state]');
      const emptyReset = document.querySelector('[data-empty-reset]');
      const laneSection = document.querySelector('[data-lane-section]');

      if (
        !(form instanceof HTMLFormElement) ||
        !(searchInput instanceof HTMLInputElement) ||
        !(surfaceSelect instanceof HTMLSelectElement) ||
        !(laneSelect instanceof HTMLSelectElement) ||
        !(status instanceof HTMLElement)
      ) {
        return;
      }

      const normalize = (value) =>
        String(value || '').normalize('NFKC').toLocaleLowerCase('ko-KR').trim();

      const selectedText = (select) =>
        select.selectedIndex > 0 ? select.options[select.selectedIndex].text.split(' · ')[0] : '';

      const setLaneChipState = (lane) => {
        laneChips.forEach((chip) => {
          const isActive = (chip.getAttribute('data-lane-chip') || '') === lane;
          chip.classList.toggle('is-active', isActive);
          chip.setAttribute('aria-pressed', String(isActive));
        });
      };

      const updateUrl = (query, surface, lane) => {
        const params = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
        if (query) params.set('q', query);
        else params.delete('q');
        if (surface) params.set('surface', surface);
        else params.delete('surface');
        if (lane) params.set('lane', lane);
        else params.delete('lane');
        const next = params.toString();
        window.history.replaceState(null, '', window.location.pathname + (next ? '?' + next : ''));
      };

      const applyFilters = (syncUrl = true) => {
        const query = normalize(searchInput.value);
        const surface = surfaceSelect.value;
        const lane = laneSelect.value;
        const tokens = query.split(/\s+/).filter(Boolean);
        let visible = 0;

        cards.forEach((card) => {
          const haystack = normalize(card.getAttribute('data-search'));
          const surfaces = (card.getAttribute('data-surfaces') || '').split(' ');
          const cardLane = card.getAttribute('data-lane') || '';
          const matchesQuery = tokens.every((token) => haystack.includes(token));
          const matchesSurface = !surface || surfaces.includes(surface);
          const matchesLane = !lane || cardLane === lane;
          const matches = matchesQuery && matchesSurface && matchesLane;
          card.hidden = !matches;
          if (matches) visible += 1;
        });

        const labelBits = [];
        if (surface) labelBits.push(selectedText(surfaceSelect));
        if (lane) labelBits.push(selectedText(laneSelect));
        if (query) labelBits.push('“' + searchInput.value.trim() + '”');
        status.textContent = (labelBits.length ? labelBits.join(' · ') : '전체') + ' ' + visible + '개';

        if (emptyState instanceof HTMLElement) emptyState.hidden = visible !== 0;
        if (laneSection instanceof HTMLElement) laneSection.hidden = Boolean(query || surface || lane);
        setLaneChipState(lane);
        if (syncUrl) updateUrl(searchInput.value.trim(), surface, lane);
      };

      const resetFilters = (focusSearch = false) => {
        searchInput.value = '';
        surfaceSelect.value = '';
        laneSelect.value = '';
        applyFilters();
        if (focusSearch) searchInput.focus();
      };

      const scrollToGrid = () => {
        document.querySelector('[data-skill-grid]')?.scrollIntoView({
          behavior: window.matchMedia('(prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)').matches ? 'auto' : 'smooth',
          block: 'start',
        });
      };

      const selectLane = (lane) => {
        laneSelect.value = lane;
        applyFilters();
        scrollToGrid();
      };

      const syncFromUrl = () => {
        const params = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
        const surface = params.get('surface') || '';
        const lane = params.get('lane') || '';
        searchInput.value = params.get('q') || '';
        surfaceSelect.value = Array.from(surfaceSelect.options).some(
          (option) => option.value === surface,
        )
          ? surface
          : '';
        laneSelect.value = Array.from(laneSelect.options).some((option) => option.value === lane)
          ? lane
          : '';
        applyFilters(false);
      };

      searchInput.addEventListener('input', () => applyFilters());
      surfaceSelect.addEventListener('change', () => applyFilters());
      laneSelect.addEventListener('change', () => applyFilters());
      form.addEventListener('submit', (event) => event.preventDefault());
      form.addEventListener('reset', (event) => {
        event.preventDefault();
        resetFilters(true);
      });

      laneChips.forEach((chip) => {
        chip.addEventListener('click', () => selectLane(chip.getAttribute('data-lane-chip') || ''));
      });
      laneShortcuts.forEach((shortcut) => {
        shortcut.addEventListener('click', () =>
          selectLane(shortcut.getAttribute('data-lane-shortcut') || ''),
        );
      });

      emptyReset?.addEventListener('click', () => resetFilters(true));
      window.addEventListener('popstate', syncFromUrl);
      document.addEventListener('keydown', (event) => {
        if (
          event.key === '/' &&
          !event.metaKey &&
          !event.ctrlKey &&
          !event.altKey &&
          !(event.target instanceof HTMLInputElement) &&
          !(event.target instanceof HTMLTextAreaElement) &&
          !(event.target instanceof HTMLSelectElement)
        ) {
          event.preventDefault();
          searchInput.focus();
        }
        if (event.key === 'Escape' && document.activeElement === searchInput && searchInput.value) {
          searchInput.value = '';
          applyFilters();
        }
      });

      syncFromUrl();
    })();
  </script>

  <style>
    .skills-page {
      --skills-accent: var(--accent);
      display: flex;
      min-width: 0;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 72px;
    }

    .skills-page > * {
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .skills-hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(280px, 380px);
      gap: 48px;
      align-items: end;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 18px 0 40px;
    }

    .eyebrow,
    .surface-summary,
    .lane-topline,
    .lane-eyebrow,
    .skill-topline,
    .skill-tag,
    .surface-list,
    .github-link,
    .catalog-toolbar,
    .update-label,
    .filter-field label,
    .lane-chip,
    .changelog,
    .skills-footer {
      font-family: var(--mono);
    }

    .eyebrow {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: var(--fg-mute);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0 0 22px;
      color: var(--fg);
      font-size: clamp(64px, 8vw, 100px);
      line-height: 0.92;
      letter-spacing: -0.055em;
    }

    .lead {
      max-width: 680px;
      color: var(--fg-dim);
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .hero-stats {
      display: grid;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--fg);
    }

    .hero-stats > div {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 80px minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: baseline;
      min-height: 62px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 15px 0;
    }

    .hero-stats dt {
      color: var(--fg-mute);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .hero-stats dd {
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
